## Notes on Training Environment

Container environment: Ubuntu 22.04, 8GB RAM, 4 vCPUs
Python version: 3.11.2
pytest version: 7.3.1
Execution timeout: 30 seconds per run

All three patterns were recorded across multiple model sizes: 7B, 13B, and 34B.

